Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要联系到你可不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not exactly an easy person to reach.
