Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  二十年来  洛克伍德钢铁被应用于\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay. For 20 years, Lockwood Steel has been used
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢瑟公司的多个成功产品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in some of Luthor Corp's most successful products.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, yeah, that is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我要提醒你的是  我们正在重塑品牌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but in case you weren't aware, we are rebranding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让L公司继续保持成功\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And in order for L-Corp to remain successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它必须跟上时代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it has to stay current.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N金属制成的钢铁才是未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Steel made with Nth metal is the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史难道不是也很重要吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shouldn't the past matter, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以这么看  你父亲可以借此机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at it this way. This is an opportunity for your father
