Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但我们工厂的机器耗费了上百万美元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, yeah, but those machines cost millions of dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲是个生意人  而且很有生意头脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your father is a businessman, and a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进步的大军行动起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just because it's the march of progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不意味着他就要被落下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}doesn't mean he has to be left behind.
