Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"西进运动"的口号  是"进步"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}during the mid 1800s. It's "Progress..."
