Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士们先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要脱稿讲点东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm gonna go off script a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进步  你们怎么看待进步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Progress. What do we think of progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有持续的发展与进步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Without continual growth and progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改善  成就与成功之类的概念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}notions such as improvement, achievement, and success,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有意义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have no meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我说的  是本·富兰克林\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not me. That's Ben Franklin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我要说的重点是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But my point is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从建国开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}ever since the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的领袖就执迷于进步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}our leaders had been obsessed with progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你能告诉我进步有什么好处吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But can you tell me what's so great about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了新大陆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, the discovery of the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是进步  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that's progress, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对西班牙和哥伦布来说是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For Spain and Columbus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对美洲原住民来说可不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No so much for the Native Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马斯丁总统的《外星人赦免法》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}President Marsdin's Alien Amnesty Act.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是进步吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为是进步  对吗  当然是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think it's progress, right? Of course, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道一些美国人不这样认为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I know some Americans who don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上  我知道一些美国人因此过得更糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In fact, I know some Americans who are worse off for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想表达什么观点呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, what's my point?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次有人告诉你进步有多伟大时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The next time someone tells you how great progress is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能停下想一想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want you to stop a moment, I want you to think
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁为进步付出了代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about who paid the price for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  下课了  都出去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, get out of here, get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生极科技事件仍未降温\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The fallout continues for Biomax Technology
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该公司上个月被曝光欺骗消费者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}exposed last month for touting a fraudulent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该设计可能致命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and possibly fatal design...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸  你怎么回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dad! What are you doing home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把它关了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-又关了一座高炉  -是整间工厂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Oh, not another blaster. - Whole factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去银行贷款  被拒绝了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He went to the bank for the loan. They said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们去死  所有人去死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hell with them and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊  爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, God, Dad, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我很遗憾  -少来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I am so sorry. - Spare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做人太软弱  不肯起身抗争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is what happens when you're too soft,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个下场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when you don't stand up and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗争  爸  和谁抗争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fight... Dad, fight who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道和谁  -那些害虫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You know who. - The roaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-乔治  -乔治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- George! - George!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我们或许积蓄不多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, we might not have much,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们还有这幢房子  我们可以...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we still have the house. We can...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以做第二抵押  我去和银行谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can get a second mortgage. I'm gonna go talk to the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈  你就只会谈  对不对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Talk. That's mostly what you do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Talk, talk, talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你真正该做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When what you should be doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出去拿出点男人样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is go out there-- and be a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸  冷静点  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dad, calm down, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人  不要惊慌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}People of Earth, do not be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为和平而来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We come in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跨越星海\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have crossed a sea of stars
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来带你们走上一条新的道路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in order to bring you a new way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接着说啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更好的道路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...A better way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧  金罗美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at that. Gin rummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定出老千了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, I'm 100% sure you're cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们情况如何  这些食物大概够吃一周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, so, what have we got? This is maybe a week of food,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限量配给的话或许够吃两周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}maybe two if we ration it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  但水就快用光了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, but we're running out of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概还能用三四天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have three, maybe four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之前没把浴缸装满水吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Didn't we fill the tub?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们或许应该离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think maybe we should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-可这是我们的家  -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- This is our home. - Yeah, it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很快就要断粮断水了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but it's quickly running out of food and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无处可去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is nowhere for us to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达克萨姆人设立了检查点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Daxamites have set up checkpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那我们能开多远开多远\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, then we drive as far as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我们能避开检查点  到沿海城市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe we can sneak around the checkpoints, get to Coast City
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们必须试试看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we have to try something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看  是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Try something? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么不试试这样  为什么不留下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How about we try this? How about we stay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为属于我们的东西抗争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we fight for what's ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的家  本  我们不是难民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is our home, Ben. We're not refugees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸  我们就在这等着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dad, just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超女会来救我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Supergirl will come and save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  她不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No! No, she won't,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为超女和那些入侵者一样是外星人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because Supergirl is an alien just like the invaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗争  爸  用什么抗争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And fight, Dad? Fight with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的全部家当都在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because all we have is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你知道吗  没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you know what? That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是一家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because we're a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以一家人齐心合力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we can come together as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸  你和乔治去拿包\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, Dad, you and Georgie get the bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪娅  去发动车子  我去拿补给品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lydia, ready the car. I'll get the supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  我们能挺过去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, listen. We can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个好男人  本·洛克伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're a good man, Ben Lockwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是个好妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not so bad yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-后退  -快走  快走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Get back! - Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的单车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's okay, it's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're safe, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:35.26,01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn微软雅黑\fs18\b0\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}凯特·格兰特新闻发布会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:35.24,01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn时尚中黑简体\fs16\an1\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad1.8\clip(73,103,37,500)\t(0,1320,\clip(73,105,367,500))\fad(0,00)\pos(75.9,238.8)}十二个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胡子  问吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, long beard, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着白宫翻修工作的开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With the White House renovations coming along,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统想把蓝屋粉刷成什么颜色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what color is the President intending to paint the Blue Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能给我拿点止痛药来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can somebody please bring me some Ibuprofen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得有点头疼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I feel a bit of a headache coming on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔森先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Olsen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊芙  你能确认一下市区银行抢劫案现场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Eve, can you make sure that we have a reporter downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有我们的记者吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for the bank robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能指望卡拉全城到处跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can't expect Kara to be everywhere, all over--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是纳市大学的洛克伍德教授\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Professor Lockwood from NCU.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记不记得他要求与你进行五分钟的会面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Remember he asked for five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你肯这么仓促地与我见面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you for seeing me on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  我总是有时间接见我们的读者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not a problem. I always have time for our subscribers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-请坐  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Please have a seat. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么能帮你的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What can I help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就直接问了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I'll just ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯特科为什么不报道外星人攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why doesn't CatCo cover the impact of extraterrestrial attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对普通公民的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on your average citizen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听你这么说我很惊讶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm surprised to hear you say that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们尽了最大的努力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because we make our best effort
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去报道每条新闻的每个侧面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to cover every side of every story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对达克萨姆人入侵以及余波的报道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And our coverage on the Daxamite invasion
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还为我们赢得了普利策奖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and its aftermath did win us a Pulitzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道  那是篇文笔优美的文章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm aware of that. It's a very beautifully-written article,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它写得好像这件事完结了似的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but it treats the story like it's over and done with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我住的社区里  人们丢了工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In my neighborhood, people have lost their jobs,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损失了财产  失去了...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}people have lost possessions, people have lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了家园\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}People have lost their homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  这周坏事频发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, it's been a hell of a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我说一些令你吃惊的事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let me just blow your mind here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,业主保险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Home owner's insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道外星人入侵其实不在保险范围内吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you know that it doesn't actually cover alien invasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谁知道呢  -我们知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Who knew? - We did,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们在商业版里报道过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because we covered that in our business section.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  但那是很久以前的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right, and that's all the way in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它把普通人变成了数字和统计数据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and it turns the common person into numbers and statistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来这是告诉你  在这些数字的背后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am here to tell you that there are people
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是活生生的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}behind these numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人正在受苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}People who are hurting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们也能报道他们的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and it would be so very helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会帮上他们的大忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if you would just tell their stories, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克伍德教授  很感谢你的立场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Professor Lockwood, I appreciate your position,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于你的遭遇  我表示遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I'm very sorry for what you've been going--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有听到我说的话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you hear anything that I--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不仅关系到我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This isn't about just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔森先生  莉娜·卢瑟打来电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Olsen, I have Lena Luthor on the line for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的谈话不得不结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have to cut this short,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你提出了一些合理的观点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but you make some valid points
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉卢瑟小姐的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I'll bring them up to Ms. Luthor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜·卢瑟  她和这些有什么关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lena Luthor. What the hell does she have to do with any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你是否听说了  她现在是这里的老板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not sure if you heard, but she runs this place now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢瑟小姐  不  我现在不忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ms. Luthor. No, I'm not busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本土主义者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nativist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.73,01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn时尚中黑简体\fs16\an1\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad1.8\clip(73,103,37,500)\t(0,1320,\clip(73,105,367,500))\fad(0,00)\pos(255.9,238.8)}六个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个常用于贬义的词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Term often used in a derogatory fashion
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来形容那些害怕外人的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to describe those who fear the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你们一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些想要保护自己家园不受外来者入侵的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's wrong with those who wish to protect their homes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有错吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from the outsiders?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国是一个移民国家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, America is a country of immigrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  但是这点一直都有争议性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, but that's always been controversial.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:20:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在1775年  本杰明·富兰克林本人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see, in 1775, Benjamin Franklin himself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写到他自己对移民的恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}writes of his own fears of immigrants whom he warned,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移民永远无法接受我们的文化或习俗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"The immigrant will never adopt our language or customs
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如他们无法获得我们的肤色一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}any more than he could acquire our complexion."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富兰克林当时说的是德国移民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Franklin was talking about German immigrants
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且当时美国还是英国的殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}back when America was still a British colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不出这话如何能套用在其他地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't see how it applies to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白这个观点为什么会有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can see why this point of view would be problematic,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是在我们说到人类移民的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}especially since we are talking about human immigrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的两百年来  无论何种肤色的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Human immigrants, who, for the past 200 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类移民成就了美国的伟大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}made America great no matter what their complexion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在  我们欢迎的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But now, we welcome immigrants
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是他国移民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not only from outside our borders,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有外星移民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but from beyond our atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我问问你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, let me just ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类工人如何与其竞争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How does the human worker compete?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.82,0:20:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能回答吗  人类工人如何与外星人竞争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anyone? How does the human worker compete against an alien
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人毫不费力地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who could lift two tons of steel
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能将两吨重的钢铁扛在肩上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}over its head without even breaking a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类工人如何与一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How does the human worker compete
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跨海岸空运货物的外星人竞争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}against an alien that can fly goods from one coast to the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们的卡车就只能放着生锈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}leaving our trucks to rust away in the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  教授  讲到哪一页了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry, Professor, what page are we on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本·富兰克林的担忧成真了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ben Franklin's fears have come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现代移民无法融入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The modern immigrant cannot assimilate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这不是意愿的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and it's not a question of desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是文化的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not a question of culture,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是生物学的问题  就此来看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it is a question of biology. And from that context...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此来看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From that context,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我本土主义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I should be proud
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会感到自豪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if you were to call me a nativist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是本土主义  这是仇外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This isn't nativism. It's xenophobia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话从你这肤色的人嘴里说出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't say I'm surprised to hear that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点也不意外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from someone with your complexion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又收到对你课程的投诉了  本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've had another complaint about your class, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这些年轻人啊  -但确实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Uh-oh. Millennials. - Still.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讲课似乎太极端了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It sounds like your lectures are extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史是极端的  真理也是极端的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, history is extreme, truth is extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:21:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课堂不是一个安全港湾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The classroom isn't a safe space
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让老师把童话版的事实讲给学生听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where everyone gets to hear a fairy tale version of the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果学生没法接受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if students can't handle perspectives
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与自己不同的观点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that are different than their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也没办法  也许他们不该在这里学习\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then I don't know. Maybe they don't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校董事会可不这么想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The tenure board would disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这是什么意思  -关于你课堂上的言论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What are you saying? - You've been warned multiple times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校已经警告你很多次了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about the rhetoric in your class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为你应该无偿离职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, we think you should take a leave of absence without pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我家里的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know what my family is going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.96,0:22:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能失去这份工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't lose this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是把你自己的偏见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're passing on your own prejudice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.72,0:22:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教给学生  本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to our students, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一所大学  一所多样化的大学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're a university, a diverse one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  我很抱歉  我一直挺喜欢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I'm sorry. I've always liked you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是你自找的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but you brought this on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃伦主任  听我说  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dean Warren, look, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢相信他们竟然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I still can't believe they haven't rounded up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没抓到从阿尔巴特洛斯湾潜逃的犯人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all those escaped convicts from Albatross Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  那疯狂哥特妹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Honestly, after that crazy goth chick
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点把他们烤焦在监狱里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}tried frying them all in their cells
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:22:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也应该休个假了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they probably deserve a little furlough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识这人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克伍德教授  你跟踪我到这来的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Professor Lockwood? Did you follow me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你告我的状吗  玻璃心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you tattle on me, Snowflake?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在说什么  行  我说你肤色的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What am I talking about? Okay, look, the complexion thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我错了  我道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, I apologize,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你非得害我被开除吗  这是我的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but you had to get me fired? This is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.03,0:23:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生计  我还要养家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is my livelihood. I have a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.49,0:23:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't say anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但别人说了也不奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I'm not surprised someone did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人  对啊  因为我实在太过分了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh! Someone. Absolutely! Because I was so out of line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看你  你不正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at you. You are not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用你同情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, I don't need your pity--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-没什么问题吧  -没\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Hey, everything okay here? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是外星人  来这里干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not an alien. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是卡拉OK之夜  我问你一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's karaoke night. Let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要唱野兽男孩的歌吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Should I do Beastie Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我能唱好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you think I could pull that off?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.55,0:23:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的话  那就唱托托的《非洲》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's either that, or Africa by Toto.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.77,0:23:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在跟你说这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not really not what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是  你是人类而他们不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm talking about you're human and they are not,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他们很危险  -你说的"他们"是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- and they are dangerous. - What do you mean by "They"?
